                        model="text-container-text"
                        modelFields="[text]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>A person’s health is influenced by more than clinical care alone. Education, access, social and environmental conditions, and financial resources all shape health outcomes — especially in underserved communities.&lt;/p>&lt;p>We work with organizations to address the root causes of systemic barriers impacting the health of their communities. By empowering our partners to accelerate and expand their innovative, community-led solutions, we’re tackling the most pressing needs and driving transformative change so everyone can thrive.&lt;/p>"/>
