                        modelFields="[text]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>The AbbVie Foundation and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.care.org/&quot; title=&quot;https://www.care.org/&quot;>CARE&lt;/a>, in partnership with &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.msm.edu/&quot; title=&quot;https://www.msm.edu/&quot;>Morehouse School of Medicine&lt;/a>, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lyft.com/&quot; title=&quot;https://www.lyft.com/&quot;>Lyft&lt;/a> and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.acfb.org/&quot; title=&quot;https://www.acfb.org/&quot;>Atlanta Community Food Bank&lt;/a>, are piloting an innovative model of care that provides complete, connected support and services to pregnant people in underserved Atlanta communities — with the aim of removing barriers and improving maternal health outcomes.&lt;/p>&lt;p>Insights from this two-year pilot will help us scale solutions to address other critical health challenges in communities across the U.S. and beyond.&lt;/p>"/>
